= Introduction =
{{Important|This slider is deprecated. You might want to use [[CT_XSLIDER]].}}
A slider can be used to make the user select a value in a predefined range.
[[Image:Arma RscSlider.jpg|thumb|Example for a CT_SLIDER control.]]
